in java inorder to create an object we have to create a class first
who creates objects in java?
its JVM -> Java Virutal Machine 

in a class we can put 2 things
->storing variables
->methods

 import java.sql.SQLOutput;

class Calculator
{
    int a = 11;
    public int add(int a,int b)
    {
        return a+b;
    }
}

public class Main
{
    public static void main(String a[])
    {
        Calculator calc = new Calculator();
        System.out.println(calc.add(3,7)); --> class{method}
        System.out.println(calc.a); --> class {variable}
    }
}
